Titolo: The Awesome Adventures of Captain Spirit

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: The Awesome Adventures of Captain Spirit (commonly shortened to Captain Spirit) is a free graphic adventure game developed by Dontnod Entertainment and published by Square Enix's European subsidiary. It was released in June 2018 for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One as an introduction to Life Is Strange 2. The plot follows Chris Eriksen, a young boy who creates the superhero alter ego Captain Spirit to deal with the loss of his mother. The game received generally favourable reviews, praising the narrative, main character, and script, but criticising the game mechanics and aspects of the writing.

Genere: Non specificato


